<paragraph blockId="36.[160,1156,823,953]" box="[160,409,823,849]" pageId="36" pageNumber="301">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,409,823,849]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="301">External morphology</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="36.[160,1156,823,953]" pageId="36" pageNumber="301">Body elongate, narrow, background colour green/yellow, dark green in parapodia, margin of parapodia wavy, white. Rhinophores short, apex white, with two white spots between eyes.</paragraph>
